name: User can open the product detail and verify that the sale status is correct

steps.name: Given I am on the main page "https://soft.reelly.io/sign-in"
When I log in to the page
And I click on "off plan" in the left side menu
And I check the sale status of the first product
And I click the first product
Then I verify that in the Details section, the sale status is correct

fullName: Verify Product Sale Status: User can open the product detail and verify that the sale status is correct
